trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de instâncias da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" />.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> a adicionar à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> to the end of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificado ao final do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index where the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> parameter has been added.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero em que o parâmetro <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> foi adicionado.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> for which to check collection membership.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> para o qual a associação da coleção é verificada.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> is a member of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna um valor que indica se o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificado é um membro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <paramref name="serviceDescription" /> parameter is a member of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o parâmetro <paramref name="serviceDescription" /> for um membro do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" />; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> serving as the destination of the copy action.
trans-unit.target: Uma matriz do tipo <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> que funciona como o destino da ação de cópia.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to start placing the copied collection.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero no qual começar a posicionar a coleção copiada.

trans-unit.source: Copies the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> to a one-dimensional array of type <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" />, starting at the specified zero-based index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia todo o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> para uma matriz unidimensional do tipo <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" />, começando no índice de base zero especificado da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" /> whose <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> property is used to retrieve a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" /> cuja propriedade <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> é usada para recuperar uma instância de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding" />.

trans-unit.source: Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> and returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding" /> with the specified name that is a member of one of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Pesquisa a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> e retorna o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Binding" /> com o nome que é um membro de uma das instâncias de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> contidas na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The binding with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: A associação com o nome especificado.

trans-unit.source: The specified <see langword="Binding" /> is not a member of any <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances within the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see langword="Binding" /> especificado não é um membro de nenhuma instância de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> dentro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" />, passed by reference, whose <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> property is shared by the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Message" /> returned.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" />, passado por referência, cuja propriedade <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> é compartilhada pelo <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Message" /> retornado.

trans-unit.source: Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> and returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Message" /> with the specified name that is a member of one of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Pesquisa a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> e retorna o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Message" /> com o nome que é um membro de uma das instâncias de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> contidas na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The message with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: A mensagem com o nome especificado.

trans-unit.source: The specified <see langword="Message" /> is not a member of any <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances within the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see langword="Message" /> especificado não é um membro de nenhuma instância de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> dentro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" />, passed by reference, whose <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> property is shared by the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortType" /> returned.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" />, passado por referência, cuja propriedade <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> é compartilhada pelo <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortType" /> retornado.

trans-unit.source: Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> and returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortType" /> with the specified name that is a member of one of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Pesquisa a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> e retorna o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.PortType" /> com o nome que é um membro de uma das instâncias de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> contidas na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see langword="PortType" /> with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: O <see langword="PortType" /> com o nome especificado.

trans-unit.source: The specified <see langword="PortType" /> is not a member of any <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances within the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see langword="PortType" /> especificado não é um membro de nenhuma instância de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> dentro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" />, passed by reference, whose <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> property is shared by the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Service" /> returned.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName" />, passado por referência, cuja propriedade <see cref="P:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName.Name" /> é compartilhada pelo <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Service" /> retornado.

trans-unit.source: Searches the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> and returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Service" /> with the specified name that is a member of one of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances contained in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Pesquisa a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> e retorna o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.Service" /> com o nome que é um membro de uma das instâncias de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> contidas na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The service with the specified name.
trans-unit.target: O serviço com o nome especificado.

trans-unit.source: The specified <see langword="Service" /> is not a member of any <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instances within the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see langword="Service" /> especificado não é um membro de nenhuma instância de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> dentro da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> for which to search in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> a ser pesquisado na coleção.

trans-unit.source: Searches for the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> and returns the zero-based index of the first occurrence within the collection.
trans-unit.target: Pesquisa o <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificado e retorna o índice de base zero da primeira ocorrência dentro de toda a coleção.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the specified service description, or -1 if the element was not found in the collection.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero da descrição de serviço especificada ou então -1, se o elemento não tiver sido encontrado na coleção.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert the <c>serviceDescription</c> parameter.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero no qual inserir o parâmetro <c>serviceDescription</c>.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> a adicionar à coleção.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instance to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> at the specified zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: Adiciona a instância de <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificada ao <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection" /> no índice de base zero especificado.

trans-unit.source: If the number of items in the collection already equals the collection's capacity, the capacity is doubled by automatically reallocating the internal array before the new element is inserted.
trans-unit.target: Se o número de itens na coleção já for igual a capacidade da coleção, a capacidade é duplicada, automaticamente realocando a matriz interna antes do novo elemento é inserido.

trans-unit.source: If the `index` parameter is equal to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, the `serviceDescription` parameter is added to the end of the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Se o `index` parâmetro for igual ao <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>, o `serviceDescription` parâmetro é adicionado ao final do <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionCollection>.

trans-unit.source: The elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: Os elementos após o ponto de inserção se mover para baixo para acomodar o novo elemento.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is less than zero.
trans-unit.target: O parâmetro <paramref name="index" /> é menor que zero.

trans-unit.source: \- or -
trans-unit.target: \- ou -

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is greater than <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />.
trans-unit.target: O parâmetro <paramref name="index" /> é maior que <see cref="P:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> instance specified by the parameter passed in.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define a instância <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificada pelo parâmetro no qual ela foi passada.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> whose value is modified or returned.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> cujo valor é modificado ou retornado.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the value of a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> at the specified zero-based index.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o valor de um <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> no índice de base zero especificado.

trans-unit.source: The value of a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: O valor de um <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> no índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: The namespace of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> returned.
trans-unit.target: O namespace do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> retornado.

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> specified by its <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.TargetNamespace" /> property.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificado por sua propriedade <see cref="P:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription.TargetNamespace" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> specified by its namespace property.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificado por sua propriedade de namespace.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> to remove from the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> a ser removido da coleção.

trans-unit.source: Removes the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Remove a primeira ocorrência do <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription" /> especificado da coleção.

trans-unit.source: This method performs a linear search; therefore, the average execution time is proportional to <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Esse método executa uma pesquisa linear; Portanto, o tempo médio de execução é proporcional ao <xref:System.Collections.CollectionBase.Count%2A>.

trans-unit.source: The elements that follow the removed <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: Os elementos que seguem o removido <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescription> mover para cima para ocupar o ponto vagas.
